    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contains the introduction, tutorial and first two bosses of Siaty's return. Get a grasp on the combination-based gameplay and challenge yourself against 3 different opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139740/extras/7f0da60aeb4e44f5f0b06e4b38f455ce.poster.avif?t=1739916706\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139740/extras/7f0da60aeb4e44f5f0b06e4b38f455ce.webm?t=1739916706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139740/extras/7f0da60aeb4e44f5f0b06e4b38f455ce.mp4?t=1739916706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master a deep combination-based gameplay   </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Siaty wields the 3 Facets of destruction, resilience and movement. In battle, these Facets can either be used separately or merged to create a wide variety of abilities. Long range attack, close range attack, dash forward, backdash, protective shield, teleportation, timed defense, ... Master Siaty's versatility and find your way to overcome whatever is in front of you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139740/extras/5ab0bb30841f90f0365962dfecdc8d2a.poster.avif?t=1739916706\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139740/extras/5ab0bb30841f90f0365962dfecdc8d2a.webm?t=1739916706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139740/extras/5ab0bb30841f90f0365962dfecdc8d2a.mp4?t=1739916706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLEASE NOTE THAT YOU NEED A CONTROLLER TO PLAY SIATY'S RETURN </h2>",
